<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to Namie Beta</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .updates {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .updates h3 {
            color: #0066cc;
        }
        .updates ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        .intro {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .sign-off {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to the Namie Beta</h1>

    <div class="updates">
        <h3>UPDATES:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Notifications working.</li>
            <li>New default picture for locations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="intro">
        <p>This app will help you remember the people you frequently bump into. Jot a name down, add a descriptor, and a picture if you love the location.</p>

        <img src="app/assets/images/StoryBoard.png" alt="Storyboard Image">

        <p>Namie will ping you the last note you wrote down at a location as you get close to it (for those nonchalant glances at your phone before engaging in conversation).</p>

        <img src="app/assets/images/App1.png" alt="App1 Image">

        <p>I designed the app to be easy to use. Text me (w/ a screenshot) if you find a weird bug!</p>

        <img src="app/assets/images/App2.png" alt="App2 Image">

        <p>Go out and meet people! Meet the owner and star employees of your favorite spots. People react differently when you remember the little things.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sign-off">
        <p>All the best,</p>
        <p>William</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
